metadata.description: Taiji Labs is more than just an NFT collection. It is an ecosystem, a brand, an identity; and ultimately an elite investment and venture capitalist-based NFT collection that invests in a wide variety of areas, such as GameFi, NFT collections, DApps, DeFi, AR, VR, data & privacy, and other blockchain-based businesses. Projects are vetted by our world-class researchers and notable web3 advisors.
